data.text: @SindiMagubane @iFarahNkosi I'm not sure of the significance of Celine Dion in capital letters??? Are we supposed to be so in awe of this woman, should I get on bended knee & kiss her feet? Utter nonsense.
@iFarahNkosi Dion now singing as many of her loyal fans sink their bank accounts & go into debt to pay exorbitant ticket prices to watch her shows. Its pure greed & totally unjustified.
